# Build-generated per-run artifacts (re-emitted by build.mjs every invocation).
# Source of truth is each run's protocol.toml + editorial.json; the rendered
# <run-dir>/report_<run-id>_<date>.html is the deliverable. Files below are
# intermediate build outputs and intentionally not tracked.
content/*.mdx
lib/runs/
lib/current-report.tsx

